    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term generally applied to ceramic products that are usually but not necessarily white, and which consist typically of clays, feldspar, potters' flint, and whiting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
